## Linking Requirements

### Internal Links (Required)

Every blog post MUST include 2-4 internal links to other StoneRise pages. These improve SEO and keep readers on the site.

**Link to these pages where relevant:**

| Page | URL | When to Link |
|------|-----|--------------|
| Procurement Product | `/products/procurement` | When discussing procurement features |
| HR Product | `/products/hr` | When discussing HR features |
| Commercial Product | `/products/commercial` | When discussing QS/commercial features |
| Request Demo | `/request-demo` | Primary CTA |
| About Us | `/about` | When mentioning StoneRise background |
| Other Blog Posts | `/blog/[slug]` | When referencing related topics |

**Internal Link Format:**

```markdown
Learn more about [construction procurement software](/products/procurement).
```

**Rules:**
- Use descriptive anchor text (not "click here" or "learn more")
- Link naturally within the content, not forced
- Place at least one internal link in the first third of the article
- CTA link at the end counts as one internal link

### External Links (Required)

Every blog post MUST include 1-3 external links to authoritative sources. These build trust and improve SEO.

**Approved External Link Sources:**

| Source Type | Examples | When to Use |
|-------------|----------|-------------|
| Industry Bodies | CIOB, RICS, Build UK, Construction Leadership Council | Industry statistics, best practices |
| Government | HSE, HMRC, gov.uk | Regulations, compliance, tax |
| Standards | ISO, British Standards | Certification, compliance references |
| Research | Deloitte, McKinsey, PwC construction reports | Industry trends, statistics |
| Trade Publications | Construction News, Building Magazine | Industry context |

**External Link Format:**

```markdown
According to [RICS guidance on procurement](https://www.rics.org/...), best practice requires...
```

**Rules:**
- Only link to authoritative, reputable sources
- Open external links in new tab (add `{:target="_blank"}` in markdown if supported)
- Never link to competitors
- Verify links are live before publishing
- Use specific pages, not homepages where possible

### Link Placement Guidelines

| Section | Internal Links | External Links |
|---------|---------------|----------------|
| Introduction | 0-1 | 0-1 |
| Body Content | 1-2 | 1-2 |
| Conclusion/CTA | 1 (demo link) | 0 |

