## Blog Post Structure

### Required Metadata Block

Every blog post must start with:

```markdown
# [Title]

> **Target Keyword:** [primary keyword]  
> **Secondary Keywords:** [2-3 secondary keywords]  
> **Target Persona:** [Commercial Leader / Finance Leader / Procurement Leader / Operations Leader]  
> **Word Count:** ~[X] words  
> **CTA:** [Request a demo / Download guide / etc.]

---

## Meta Description

[150-160 character meta description including target keyword]

---
```

### Required Sections

1. **Introduction** (150-200 words)
   - Hook with the problem
   - Brief answer to the title question
   - Promise what the article covers

2. **Body Content** (800-1,200 words)
   - Clear H2 and H3 structure
   - Short paragraphs (2-4 sentences)
   - Bullet points and tables where helpful
   - Include target keyword in at least one H2

3. **Conclusion** (100-150 words)
   - Summarise key points
   - Reinforce the main benefit

4. **CTA Section** (50-100 words)
   - Clear call to action
   - Link with UTM parameters

5. **FAQ Section** (Optional but recommended)
   - 3-5 questions
   - Direct answers (featured snippet format)

