## CTA Link Format

All blog CTAs must use proper UTM parameters:

```
https://www.stonerise.tech/request-demo?utm_source=blog&utm_medium=organic_search&utm_campaign=[keyword]_[product]&utm_content=blog_cta
```

**Example:**
```
https://www.stonerise.tech/request-demo?utm_source=blog&utm_medium=organic_search&utm_campaign=three_way_matching_procurement&utm_content=blog_cta
```

---

## SEO Checklist

Before publishing, verify:

- [ ] Target keyword in title (H1)
- [ ] Target keyword in meta description
- [ ] Target keyword in at least one H2
- [ ] Target keyword in first 100 words
- [ ] 2-4 internal links included
- [ ] 1-3 external links to authoritative sources
- [ ] No em dashes used
- [ ] CTA with UTM parameters
- [ ] Word count meets minimum (800+ words)
- [ ] FAQ section included (recommended)

